.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, cooking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Hobby         | card-games | cooking     |
| Birthday   | august  | march         |

